# Keep `railway up` uploads lean. The API image only needs the pnpm workspace
# (apps/api, apps/console, apps/arcade, packages/*). Everything below is rebuilt
# in-image, hosted elsewhere (Godot games live on R2), or raw source art.
#
# IMPORTANT: anchor directory excludes with a leading "/". An unanchored name
# like `games` matches at EVERY level and would wrongly drop apps/api/src/games.

# Build + dependency artifacts (regenerated during the image build).
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/coverage
.git

# Godot game projects + builds — hosted on Cloudflare R2, not part of the API build.
/games

# Raw source art the owner keeps locally (not used by any build).
/assets
/Screenshot*.png
